OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fclear evening leading into a chilly
OL,7,Fnight, but clouding over towards dawn,
OL,8,Fwith a few showers moving towards
OL,9,FShetland, freshening southerly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FMainly dry with just a few
OL,12,Fshowers in the morning. Rain reaching
OL,13,FOrkney early afternoon, and Shetland
OL,14,Flate afternoon. Fresh to strong south
OL,15,Fto southeasterly winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA wet
OL,18,Fstart to the new week but rain
OL,19,Fclearing later on Monday. Dry and
OL,20,Fsettled conditions developing on
OL,21,FTuesday and Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
